Tango Organic Pelleted Celery Seed

Product ID:647GP.54647GP

Highly adaptable variety with great flavor and tender stalks. Tango performs well under less than ideal growing conditions such as heat or moisture stress. USDA Certified Organic. Avg. 11,300 seeds/oz. Packet: 250 seeds.

Caution:
In rare instances, contact with the foliage can result in a severe rash. When working with this crop on hot, sunny days, we recommend wearing long sleeves and long pants, and washing any exposed skin surfaces as soon as possible after contact.
